    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "guard_body",
      "x": 340, "y": 1062,
      "width": 520, "height": 150,
      "text": "•  dryRun (default true) gates every GitHub write & push\n•  Approve is the sole write path — a change pushes only on\n    your click; risk:\"high\" always vetoes auto-push\n•  fast-forward-only push; serial per-repo queue\n•  never act on a GitHub-resolved Thread (checked twice)\n•  ignoreRepos / ignoreAuthors resolve without a verdict\n•  gh CLI is the only GitHub surface — no token path",
      "originalText": "•  dryRun (default true) gates every GitHub write & push\n•  Approve is the sole write path — a change pushes only on\n    your click; risk:\"high\" always vetoes auto-push\n•  fast-forward-only push; serial per-repo queue\n•  never act on a GitHub-resolved Thread (checked twice)\n•  ignoreRepos / ignoreAuthors resolve without a verdict\n•  gh CLI is the only GitHub surface — no token path",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#e2e8f0", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
